[[File:Mandoviol.jpg|thumb|right|250px|A mandoviol.]]
The '''mandoviol''' was a stringed [[Music/Legends|musical]] instrument popular with [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] [[Band/Legends|bands]] across [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] during the era of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. With seventeen minor keys, four major keys, and a slide attachment, the mandoviol was a difficult instrument to master, but could be used to play ballads as well as energetic [[Jizz/Legends|jizz]] tunes with equal aplomb.

